How to cite / attribute
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
When reusing this work, please cite the associated dataset and publication as
described in CITATION.cff and README.md, e.g.:

  Kruger, R., Els, P. S., & Hamersma, H. A. (2023). Experimental investigation
  of factors affecting the characterisation of soil strength properties using a
  Bevameter in-situ plate sinkage and shear test apparatus. Journal of
  Terramechanics, 109, 45-62. https://doi.org/10.1016/j.jterra.2023.06.002

  Kruger, R. (2026). Geotechnical Test Data Repository: Bevameter plate
  sinkage, shear tests, and triaxial tests [Data set]. Zenodo.
  DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.17584462

